programming, irc, cars

Second I’ll let this one slide and I’ll help you out with this one. I happen to have a berky-scape source lieing around so heres my compiler code.

@echo off Title Berky-Scape Compiler cd .. "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_13\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ./Bin/ ./Bulby/./io/*.java pause

where it says

jdk1.6.0_13

the 13 would be the version of your java. So if you have jdk 6update12 you would change the 13 to 12 and so on and so forth.

IF you still don’t understand post back and I’ll solve it.
